      <title>新西兰因“不可持续”移民收紧工人签证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/new-zealand-tightens-worker-visas-over-unsustainable-migration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰政府立即对就业签证计划进行了修改，理由是“不可持续”的净移民，并指出了进一步的潜在变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/new-zealand-tightens-worker-visas-over-unsustainable-migration</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 01:09:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克向法院提起诉讼，取消对巴西 X 账户的限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/musk-lifts-restrictions-on-x-accounts-in-brazil-in-challenge-to-courts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克表示，他将取消对巴西部分 X 账户的限制，即使此举会导致该国社交媒体平台关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/musk-lifts-restrictions-on-x-accounts-in-brazil-in-challenge-to-courts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 00:26:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国带头推动六国签证以吸引有钱的游客</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/thailand-leads-push-for-six-nation-visa-to-lure-moneyed-tourists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维辛 (Srettha Thavisin) 加大力度吸引更多长途旅行和高消费游客，泰国正在与去年共接待游客约 7000 万的国家制定联合签证计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/thailand-leads-push-for-six-nation-visa-to-lure-moneyed-tourists</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯友好领导人的盟友赢得斯洛伐克总统选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/ally-of-russia-friendly-premier-fico-wins-presidential-election-in-slovakia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亲俄罗斯的总理罗伯特·菲科坚决反对对乌克兰提供军事援助，在他的盟友赢得斯洛伐克总统选举后，他将巩固自己对权力的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/ally-of-russia-friendly-premier-fico-wins-presidential-election-in-slovakia</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 22:44:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>总理的盟友有望赢得斯洛伐克总统选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/premier-s-ally-on-track-to-win-slovak-presidential-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯洛伐克总理罗伯特·菲科的盟友有望赢得该国总统选举，这将有助于巩固总理对权力的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/premier-s-ally-on-track-to-win-slovak-presidential-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:33:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国将部署皇家海军向加沙地带运送食品和补给</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/uk-to-deploy-royal-navy-to-deliver-food-supplies-to-gaza-strip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在以色列军事袭击造成三名英国援助人员死亡几天后，英国将部署一艘皇家海军舰艇，以增加对加沙的人道主义支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/uk-to-deploy-royal-navy-to-deliver-food-supplies-to-gaza-strip</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔因袭击墨西哥大使馆而遭到拉丁美洲各地的谴责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/ecuador-rebuked-across-latin-america-for-raid-on-mexican-embassy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔政府因冲进墨西哥大使馆逮捕一名前副总统而遭到拉丁美洲各地的谴责，此举违反了外交礼仪，总统丹尼尔·诺博亚将其与打击犯罪团伙和卡特尔的斗争联系在一起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/ecuador-rebuked-across-latin-america-for-raid-on-mexican-embassy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:28:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国警告中国向俄罗斯提供地理空间情报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/china-is-providing-geospatial-intelligence-to-russia-us-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国警告盟友，中国已加大对俄罗斯的支持，包括提供地理空间情报，以帮助莫斯科对抗乌克兰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/china-is-providing-geospatial-intelligence-to-russia-us-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 13:21:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登筹集9000万美元，扩大筹款领先特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/biden-2024-campaign-raises-90m-beating-trump-with-record-192m-on-hand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[3月份，美国总统乔·拜登为其连任竞选活动和民主党筹集了超过9000万美元，超过了共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普，并扩大了他的财务优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/biden-2024-campaign-raises-90m-beating-trump-with-record-192m-on-hand</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ZiG 推出前津巴布韦的银行服务中断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/zimbabwe-s-currency-banking-disrupted-ahead-of-zig-usd-zwl-launch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于银行急于将所有津巴布韦美元账户余额转换为津巴布韦储备银行行长约翰·穆沙亚万胡 (John Mushayavanhu) 宣布的新法定货币 ZiG，津巴布韦各地的银行业受到干扰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/zimbabwe-s-currency-banking-disrupted-ahead-of-zig-usd-zwl-launch</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 10:23:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
